even that ridiculous processor and RAM config.</p><p>On my T3500 Dreamweaver, Fireworks, etc. booted from scratch in about 2.5 seconds the first time, 0 subsequent times. It felt like Windows 7 Pro 64 booted in a yawn and a half. So worth the money.</p></div>
